msgid "Multi-Platform"
msgstr ""

#. home.multiplatform.text1
#: i18n/en.yaml:84
msgid ""
"Develop once, deploy everywhere. Built on top of Qt, KDE's technologies work "
"on every platform."
msgstr ""

#. home.multiplatform.text2
